{% comment %}
  - https://help.shopify.com/en/themes/development/templates/collection-liquid
  - Limit of 50 products per page.
      - If the design of the page is 2/3/4 images wide, in order to have all
        images on interim pages to frame the page completely, we want pages to
        paginate at counts of 12n: 12/24/36/48/60/72/84/96/...
      - Paginate at 48 items.
  - To add sorting: https://gist.github.com/carolineschnapp/11352987
  - Show all tags used within a collection, or create a collection for each tag and create a deeply nested hierarchy for the menu.
  - We show {style,color} items in each collection.  This allows us to:
      - Create a "Styled/Paired With" set for each {style,color} pair.
      - Create an "Other Colors" set, if applicable.
      - Create an "Other of Same Type" set (e.g. Tunics, or Long Sleeve Blouses).
      - Fill the Browse pages with more content.
      - Allows us to use different outfits for a style's colors.

